@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004

### REST - Get All Categories (entity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/rest/Categories

###

### REST - getCategories action
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/rest/getCategories
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### OData - Get All Categories (entity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/odata/v4/odata/Categories

###

### OData - getCategories action
POST {{baseUrl}}/odata/v4/odata/getCategories
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### REST - Upload CSV file
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/rest/uploadFile
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

ID,name,age
1,Alice,30
2,Bob,25
--boundary--

###

### REST - Get all uploaded files
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/rest/FileUploads
